    "en": {
      "title": "SLAF denies reports that President staying at Air Chief\u2019s private residence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Air Force (SLAF) today denied social media reports that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is currently staying in a private house belonging to Air Force Chief Air Marshal Sudarshana Pathirana.",
        "The SLAF said a video released by Ajith Dharmapala, a former police officer who claims to be the president of the International Organization to Devoid Sri Lankan Police from Politics, claimed that the President is staying in a private house belonging to the Air Force Commander.",
        "The SLAF Spokesman Dushan Wijesinghe said that there is no truth behind the reports and it was a propaganda to tarnish the image of the SLAF and its chief.(Darshana Sanjeewa Balasuriya)"
      ],
